00:04:37.800 --> 00:04:40.320
[Amit Varma]: Shruti, welcome to the scene in the unseen.

00:04:40.320 --> 00:04:41.320
[Amit Varma]: Hi, Amit.

00:04:41.320 --> 00:04:48.200
[Amit Varma]: Shruti, I've started this new tradition on my shows of just chatting with my guests and

00:04:48.200 --> 00:04:52.320
[Amit Varma]: asking them a few personal questions, so the listeners can get to know them a little better.

